cdata.name: Menlo One
cdata.desc:
Menlo One is an open-source framework for making Dapps(Decentralized Applications). It provides the users with a set of tools and protocolsto assist them in creating and developing Dapps. At Menlo One, developers are able tobuild Web 3.0 generation of marketplaces, social media platforms, DAOs, financial products, and other Dapps variants.

The ONE token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is a utility token thatcan serve the users when paying nodes for data availability, others users attention, and/or comments and reviews.
